description: Exceptional 4-story townhouse crafted by renowned architect Utile Inc. This residence provides the comfort of a single-family home with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, private outdoor space, and an exclusive TWO car garage. The European-inspired chef's kitchen by Aster Cucine boasts Stainless Bosch appliances, quartz countertops, and bespoke cabinetry. The first floor features an open-concept kitchen/living room with oak hardwood floors, expansive floor-to-ceiling windows, a gas fireplace, and a convenient office nook. On the second floor, discover two bedrooms with custom-built in closets along adjoining bathroom featuring double sinks and marble shower. Top floor house the primary suite featuring an en-suite bathroom and sliders leading to a private deck. The deck is equipped with a direct gas line for grilling and water supply for plants. Additional highlights include mudroom, laundry room, NEST thermostats and surround sound speakers.
